 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\">Von Carstein:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\">@Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-traits.HlglLURNjR5c1GBa]{No Reflection},&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\">@Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-traits.Q7MlIkwCwpGf7Uoc]{Religious Symbols},&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\">@Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-traits.XK2jviw2VtiUS3Ib]{Running Water},&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\">@Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-traits.ST53lU8ZAcG8cHE1]{Silver}, </span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\">@Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-traits.GlNKrHp857Epq8zU]{Soil Sleeper}</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\">Independent:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\">@Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-traits.2MOzsTr8s1YrAJKf]{Daemonsroot and Witchbane},&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\">@Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-traits.HlglLURNjR5c1GBa]{No Reflection},&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\">@Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-traits.Q7MlIkwCwpGf7Uoc]{Religious Symbols},&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\">@Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-traits.XK2jviw2VtiUS3Ib]{Running Water},&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\">@Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-traits.ST53lU8ZAcG8cHE1]{Silver}</span></p>"}
{"_id":"LM32MzJyJWy32Gl8","name":"Ghoul Master","permission":{"default":0,"kHr5wGqy2Rw4go1y":3},"flags":{},"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>&lsquo;You find my face terrifying? Does it remind you of the beast inside yourself? Here, let me free it!&rsquo;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&ndash; Diskittar the Swollen</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Ghoul Kings are Strigoi who revel in their disturbing forms.</h3>\n<p>They feed from the dead, dwelling in crypts and graveyards, hiding from their more Human kin &mdash; whom they despise for their pretentions. The Ghoul Kings have no delusions of grandeur; they are what they are. As befits their name, they command legions of Ghouls and other ghastly minions, and prefer to take the form of the bat when they transform.</p>\n<p>Ghoul Kings are often Necromancers, but they occasionally learn a Dhar-infused version of the Lore of Beasts, whereby they summon vermin and serpents, commanding the fouler creatures that stalk their graveyards and cavernous lairs. Though the Ghoul Kings lack the warped chivalry of the Blood Dragons, they are exceptional warriors nonetheless.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Species:&nbsp;</strong>Vampire</p>\n<p><strong>Class: </strong>Ranger</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Ghoul Master Advance Scheme</h3>\n<table style=\"height: 34px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">WS</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">BS</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">S</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">T</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">Agi</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">Dex</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">Int</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">WP</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">Fel</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">III</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">II</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">IV</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 61px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3><strong>I. @Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-careers.8YF0LlK1PN8NXqEZ]{Ghoul Brother}</strong></h3>\n<h3><strong>II. @Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-careers.2bbsWMhU9bq3JxiE]{Ghoul Master}</strong></h3>\n<h3><strong>III. @Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-careers.ReiHYsNpfP1L1F6P]{Ghoul Lord}</strong></h3>\n<h3><strong>IV. @Compendium[wfrp4e-vampires.vampires-careers.yNG2lNzqtqpjyjOH]{Ghoul King}</strong></h3>\n<p><br /><br /></p>","img":""}
